<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Hello!</h2>
    <p>
      <b><%= @inviter.full_name || @inviter.email %></b> has invited you to join SplitHive.
    </p>

    <p>
      SplitHive helps friends and groups track shared expenses and settle balances.
    </p>

    <p>
      Use the link below to create your account. This invitation is only for joining SplitHive and will not add you to any group automatically.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= @url %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background-color:#0d6efd;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;">Create your SplitHive account</a>
    </p>

    <p>Thanks for using SplitHive!</p>
  </body>
</html>
